To create fixtures from existing test data run:
./mg.sh "dumpdata  --indent=2" > fixtures/fixtures_all.json

to dump a single app

./mg.sh "dumpdata app_label --indent=2 > fixtures/fixtures_app_label.json"

to dump single model 

./mg.sh "dumpdata app_label.model --indent=2 > fixtures/fixtures_model.json"

Example:
To recreate permissions for testing:
./mg.sh "dumpdata auth --indent=2 > fixtures/fixtures_auth.json"
./mg.sh "dumpdata django.content_type --indent=2 > fixtures/fixtures_content_type.json"
Then open file and delete first line
Congratulations, you just fixtured

to load fixture data into dev db
./mg.sh "loaddata fixtures/fixtures_all.json"